INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (233,'199900102001','a) Let $$f(x)=2x^4+5x^2-7$$;When f(x) is divided by x + 3,;Remainder = f(- 3);= $$2(-3)^4+5(-3)^2-7=200$$ (ANS);  b)$$2x^3+5x^2-6x-5-=(Ax-3)(x+B)(x+1)+C$$;Comparing coefficient of $$x^3$$;2 = A;A = 2;Comparing coefficient of $$x^2$$;5 = A - 3 + AB;   = 2 - 3+2B;   B = 3;Comparing cons\\tan t,;- 5 = -3B + C; = - 3(3) + C;C = 4;Therefore A = 2, B = 3, C = 4 (ANS);c)i) Let $$g(x)=7x^2+35$$ and;$$h(x)=44x-2x^3$$;When g(x) is divided by x - p,;Remainder = g(p);When h(x) is divided by x - p,;Remainder = h(p);g(p) = h(p);$$7p^2+35=44p-2p^3$$;$$2p^3+7p^2-44p+35=0$$;Let;$$f(p)=2p^3+7p^2-44p+35$$;f(1) = 0;Therefore p - 1 is a factor ;$$2p^3+7p^2-44p+35=0$$;$$(p-1)(2p^2+9p-35)=0$$;$$(p-1)(2p-5)(p+7)=0$$;$$p=-7,1, 2 \\frac{1}{2}$$ (ANS);ii) Remainder  = $$7p^2+35$$;when p = - 7,;Remainder  = $$7(-7)^2+35=378$$;when p = 1;$$7(1)^2+35=42$$;when p = $$2\\frac{1}{2}$$;Remainder = $$7(2\\frac{1}{2})^2+35=78.75$$;Therefore the largest remainder is 378, when p = - 7 (ANS)');
