INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (327,'200100101007','i) $$v=t^3-3t^2+2t$$;$$a=\\frac{\\mathrm{d} v}{\\mathrm{d} t}=3t^2-6t+2$$;at t = 1.5,;$$a=3(1.5)^2-6(1.5)+2=-0.25 \\frac{m}{s^2}$$ (ANS);ii) $$v=0$$;$$t^3-3t^2+2t=0$$;$$t(t^2-3t+2)=0$$;$$t(t-2)(t-1)=0$$;$$t=0,t=1,t=2$$ (ANS);iii) $$s=\\int vdt$$;$$\\int (t^3-3t^2+2t)dt$$;=$$\\frac{ (t^4)}{4}-t^3+t^2+c$$;When t = 0, s = 0;Therefore c = 0;$$s=\\frac{t^4}{4}-t^3+t^2$$;t = 1, s = 0.25;t = 2, s = 0;Therefore distance = 0.25 m x 2 = 0.5 m (ANS)');
