INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (349,'200100103003','i) Let P be (m, n);Using similar Triangle S,;$$ \\frac{5}{m}=\\frac{5}{2}$$;$$\\Rightarrow m=2$$;Gradient of AP = Gradient of AB;$$ \\frac{ (11-n)}{(5-2)}= \\frac{ (11-0)}{(5-0)}$$;$$\\Rightarrow 11-n=3(2)$$;$$n=5$$;Therefore, P(2, 5);ii) $$\\angle PCQ= \\angle PQC \\Rightarrow PC = PQ$$ (isosceles triangle);Therefore gradient of PQ = - gradient of PC = - 2;Equation of PQ:;$$y-5=-2(x-2)$$;$$\\Rightarrow y-5=-2x+4$$;$$y=-2x+9$$;iii) PQ cuts x-axis,;when;$$y=0 \\Rightarrow -2x+9=0$$;$$2x=9$$;$$x= \\frac{9}{2}$$;Therefore Q is (4.5, 0) (ANS)');
