INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (528,'200500104012','(i) $$y = 2\\cos (x) - \\cos (2x)$$;$$\\frac{\\mathrm{d} y}{\\mathrm{d} x}=-2\\sin (x)+2\\sin (2x)$$ (ANS);$$ \\frac{\\mathrm{d} ^{2}y}{\\mathrm{d} x^{2}}=-2\\cos (x)+4\\cos (2x)$$ (ANS);(ii) At the stationary point  , $$\\frac{\\mathrm{d} y}{\\mathrm{d} x}=0$$;$$-2\\sin (x)+2\\sin (2x)=0$$;$$-2\\sin (x)+4\\sin (x)\\cos (x)=0$$;$$-2\\sin (x)(1-2\\cos (x))=0$$;$$\\sin (x)=0(N.A) or \\cos (x)=\\frac{1}{2} \\Rightarrow x = -\\frac{\\pi}{3}$$;When $$x = -\\frac{\\pi}{3}$$,;$$\\frac{\\mathrm{d} ^{2}y}{\\mathrm{d} x^{2}}=-2\\cos (\\frac{\\pi}{3})+4\\cos (\\frac{ (2\\pi )}{3})$$;  = -3 < 0;The stationary point   at $$x=-\\frac{\\pi}{3}$$ is a max point  . (ANS);(iii) $$\\int _{\\frac{\\pi}{3}}^{(\\frac{\\pi}{2})}ydx$$;=$$\\int _{\\frac{\\pi}{3}}^{(\\frac{\\pi}{2})}(2\\cos (x)-\\cos (2x))dx$$;=$$[2\\sin (x)- \\frac{ (\\sin (2x))}{x}]_{\\frac{\\pi}{3}}^{(\\frac{\\pi}{2})}$$;=$$2\\sin (\\frac{\\pi}{2})-\\frac{ (\\sin (\\pi ))}{2}-2\\sin (\\frac{\\pi}{3})+\\frac{ (\\sin (\\frac{ (2\\pi )}{3}))}{2}$$;=$$2-0-2 \\times  \\sqrt {\\frac{3}{2}} + \\sqrt {\\frac{3}{4}}$$;=$$2-\\frac{ (3\\sqrt 3)}{4}$$ ;=0.701 (ANS)');
INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (529,'200500104013','(i) Gradient of ST= $$\\frac{15}{3.75}$$ = -4;$$y=x^2-10x+24$$;$$\\frac{\\mathrm{d} y}{\\mathrm{d} x}=2x-10$$;2x - 10 = -4;x = 3;Sub x=3 into $$y=x^2-10x+24$$;y = 9 - 30 + 24;y = 3;The coordinates of p = (3, 3) (ANS);(ii) Equation of the normal to the curve at P is given by;$$y-3=\\frac{1}{4}(x-3)$$;$$y=\\frac{1}{4}x+\\frac{9}{4}$$;When y=0,;$$\\frac{1}{4}x+\\frac{9}{4}=0$$;x = - 9 ;Coordinates of R = (-9, 0). (ANS);(iii) Shaded area;=$$\\frac{1}{2} \\times  12 \\times  3 + \\int _2^4(x^2-10x+24)dx$$;=$$18+[\\frac{x^3}{3}-5x^2+24x]_3^4$$;=$$18+6\\frac{4}{3}-80+96-9=45-72$$;=$$19 \\frac{1}{3} units^2$$ (ANS)');
